import React from 'react'

import { Wrapper, Content } from './styles'

import Card from './Card/index'

const CardList = () => {
  return (
    <Wrapper>
      <Content>
        <Card
          imgSrc='/goochIcon.png'
          imgAlt='Gooch'
          title='Few Characters'
          text="When social media sites such as Twitter give you character limits you've gotta be resourcful."
        />
        <Card
          imgSrc='/goochIcon.png'
          imgAlt='Gooch'
          title='Promote Sharing'
          text="Big links are scary, give out shorter links so people that people arn't confused on what they are clicking."
        />
        <Card
          imgSrc='/goochIcon.png'
          imgAlt='Gooch'
          title='More Clicks'
          text='People are used to shortened links so they should be provided with them in order to get clicks.'
        />
      </Content>
    </Wrapper>
  )
}

export default CardList
